{"word":"G2155 - εὔσπλαγχνος - eúsplanchnos - yoo'-splangkh-nos - Pitiful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὔσπλαγχνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eúsplanchnos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo'-splangkh-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pitiful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மனஉருக்கமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"compassionate, tender - hearted"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G4698 - σπλάγχνον - splánchnon - splangkh'-non/4698\">G4698</a>; <i>well compassioned</i>, that is, <i>sympathetic:</i> - pitiful, tender-hearted.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2155/2155\">G2155</a>, <a href=\"#/G4184/4184\">G4184</a>, <a href=\"#/G4697/4697\">G4697</a>, <a href=\"#/G4698/4698\">G4698</a>"}]}